OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fclear night to come with perhaps a few
OL,7,Fmist and fog patches. Breezy around
OL,8,Fcoasts. A chilly night with perhaps a
OL,9,Ftouch of frost in the countryside.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA pleasant day on Tuesday
OL,12,Fwith lots of sunshine, although skies
OL,13,Fmay turn hazy across western areas by
OL,14,Fthe afternoon. Breezy around coasts.
OL,15,FFeeling warm, especially in the
OL,16,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
