OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FLargely dry with warm spells of
OL,7,Fsunshine on Wednesday. Turning cooler
OL,8,Fand more changeable from Thursday with
OL,9,Fspells of rain and showers moving
OL,10,Facross the region.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
